PrecisAmendment to the IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 adding the newly-independent country of Namibia to Schedule II, thereby allowing nationals of that country to enter Canada without first obtaining a visitor's visa.

precis:
Amendment to the IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 adding the
newly-independent country of Namibia to Schedule II, thereby allowing
nationals of that country to enter Canada without first obtaining a
visitor's visa.
